cs.LG, cs.CE, cs.TR, cs.DS, cs.MA 

This paper involves the use of machine learning methods for mid-price forecasting in high-frequency financial markets. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely categories include cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science), cs.TR (Trading and Market Microstructure), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems).
